    <section id="id16370865">
      <title>Assessment</title>
      <para id="id16370361"><emphasis>Learning Outcome 4: </emphasis>The learner will be able to use appropriate measuring units, instruments and formulae in a variety of contexts.</para>
      <para id="id16370232"><emphasis>Assessment Standard 4.6:</emphasis> We know this when the learner uses appropriate measuring instruments (with understanding of their limitations) to appropriate levels of precision including:</para>
      <para id="id16369634"><emphasis effect="bold">4.6.1: </emphasis>bathroom scales, kitchen scales and balances to measure mass.</para>
    </section>
